LIZ HELDENS: I'm a writer.

00:02:30.432 --> 00:02:32.765
SETH MACFARLANE: You're an
executive producer, too, Liz,

00:02:32.765 --> 00:02:33.160
for god's sakes.

00:02:33.160 --> 00:02:34.140
LIZ HELDENS: Executive producer.

