We were trying to do the
count of how many prosthetic

00:10:49.660 --> 00:10:50.534
make ups we had done.

00:10:50.534 --> 00:10:51.670
And it's over 5,000.

00:10:51.670 --> 00:10:53.740
Playing every single
day was more exciting

00:10:53.740 --> 00:10:55.196
than you could ever imagine.

