seems to be, look,

00:22:17.700 --> 00:22:20.130
we don't know where
the industry is going.

00:22:20.130 --> 00:22:24.150
You don't lose any more by
trying to be different and new

00:22:24.150 --> 00:22:27.450
and do something that nobody
else is doing, so let's try it.

