00:25:42.800 --> 00:25:46.460
The idea of the Krill being
a technologically advanced

00:25:46.460 --> 00:25:50.580
species that still clings
to their religion very,

00:25:50.580 --> 00:25:56.030
very heavily is something that
this way I hadn't seen before.

00:25:56.030 --> 00:26:00.140
And it's trying to
find new ways to,

00:26:00.140 --> 00:26:04.200
look, the basis of your
series is the universe.

00:26:04.200 --> 00:26:06.459
